In this directory, there is a set for executing the playbook
to install Zabbix Agent 2 via SSH on any number of hosts
running Windows 10/2019 or later. To correctly execute the playbook,
you need to adjust the playbook file and the hosts file to your
specific values (paths, IP addresses, etc.). Prior to that,
you need to execute the openssh_install.ps1 script from the
install_agent.zip archive if OpenSSH is not yet installed
and not configured on the target host.
